    TrustScore --> Settings : reads thresholds
    F008 --> TrustScore : caches by spiffe_id
    F009 --> TrustScore : reads score
    F027 --> TrustScore : creates from history
    F028 --> TrustScore : recalibrates score
    F029 --> TrustScore : propagates along chain

    note for TrustScore "Category bands:\nHigh >= settings.trust_threshold\nMedium >= 0.4\nLow < 0.4\n\nafter_violation returns new frozen object"
